text: Ani hamile ti manisaharula'i yasa kitabako uttaradhikari banayaum, jasala'i aphna sevakaharumadhye rojyaum. Uniharumadhye kehi ta aphainle aphumathi atyacara gardachan ra uniharumadhye kehi madhyama srenika chan ra allahako adesale tiniharumadhye kehi asala karmama vrd'dhi gardai ga'irahanchan. Yahi nai thulo upakara ho
